Insider Activity


Individual




John J. Zillmer



Mr. John J. Zillmer is President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Univar, Inc. and an Advisor at Liberty Capital Partners, Inc. (Rhode Island). He is on the Board of Directors at Univar, Inc., Reynolds American, Inc., and Ecolab, Inc.
Mr. Zillmer was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Allied Waste Industries, Inc. and Executive Vice President by ARAMARK Corp. He also served on the board at Pathmark Stores, Inc., United Stationers, Inc., and Casella Waste Systems, Inc.
Mr. Zillmer received his MBA from Northwestern University.



